<p><a id="page#87094#link" title="Sidetype:                	ListesideOpprettet:               	14.11.2006 10:20:00Endret:                  	14.11.2006 10:25:32Sidens ID:               	87094Sorteringsindeks:        	100" href="/en/dep/smk/documents/The-Speech-from-the-Throne.html?id=87094" pageacl="63" pagelink="87094" action="LoadPage('87094');">The Speech from the Throne</a>&nbsp;expresses the main lines of the Government's policy for the coming year.</p>
<p><a id="page#87168#link" title="Sidetype:                	ListesideOpprettet:               	14.11.2006 10:57:00Endret:                  	14.11.2006 10:59:21Sidens ID:               	87168Sorteringsindeks:        	200" href="/en/dep/smk/documents/The-Report-on-the-State-of-the-Realm.html?id=87168" pageacl="63" pagelink="87168" action="LoadPage('87168');">The Report on the State of the Realm</a>&nbsp;The report covers the Government's policy over the past year, presenting what have been achieved and important proposals that have been launched. (in Norwegian only)&nbsp;</p>
